	   <tr><td colspan=2>Earth, Earth, and Earth. With the ability to root, this pet keeps you safe from the mob running to its buddies. When your in a group, it keeps the mob from running to its buddies. And, when your in a doungon, root keeps your mog in place so it doesnt pull its buddies. What can the water pet do? A minor spell? Yeah but what about when the mob runs to another friend and then ya die. Happened alot with me. Then I turned level 5 hehe. Make the smart choice and vote for earth element for mage pet =)<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp; Sumren Starstone<br>   ctu, gnome mage, 39<br>   "Kick the Halfing! Not the Gnome!"<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
